title: Mystery Archive of Thunder
story: The archive is situated on a remote island. These days it is infested by snakes, which don't care about the past of the place.

notes.text: A rear entrance into the archive. A mouth-shaped gate with a keyhole to the east.
A weird, singing spear among rubble on the ground.
A corpse of a goblin, an ornate katana, lockpicks and some gold nearby.
A large chest containing a cape.
A magic doll on a pedestal table.
